{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make the school weekend Wednesday and Sunday, not Saturday and Sunday",
        "additional_details": "We believe changing how the school weekend works could help increase productivity and concentration for students, and reduce the negative feelings many people have on Sunday, when they realise the weekend is almost over.",
        "background": "We want schools to be required to close for the weekend on Wednesday and Sunday, and be open Monday and Tuesday, then Thursday, Friday and Saturday.",
